A — Simple search (GET)

GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products/search?keyword=Hydrating

GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products/search?keyword=lipstick

GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products/search?keyword=Cherry

GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products/search?keyword=serum

GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products/search?keyword=Maybelline

B — Synonym search (GET)

(Uses synonyms analyzer + synonyms field; try these)

GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products/synonym-search?keyword=lip%20gloss

GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products/synonym-search?keyword=elixir

GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products/synonym-search?keyword=fragrance

GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products/synonym-search?keyword=moisturiser

GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products/synonym-search?keyword=hair%20wash

C — Faceted search (GET) — multiple brands/colors via repeated param

Examples:

GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products/faceted-search?keyword=hydrating&brand=Nykaa&brand=MAC&color=Pink&priceMin=200&priceMax=1200&ratingMin=3&ratingMax=5

GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products/faceted-search?category=Moisturizer

GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products/faceted-search?color=Gold&color=Silver

GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products/faceted-search?keyword=shampoo&priceMax=500

GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products/faceted-search?keyword=lipstick&ratingMin=4

D — Enhanced search (GET) — multi filters + pagination

Examples (use repeated brands / colors to pass lists):

GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products/enhanced-search?keyword=hydrating&category=Moisturizer&brands=Nykaa&brands=L'Oreal&colors=Pink&priceMin=200&priceMax=1500&ratingMin=4&limit=20&offset=0

GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products/enhanced-search?keyword=serum&limit=10&offset=0

GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products/enhanced-search?brands=MAC&brands=Clinique&colors=Gold&limit=25&offset=0

GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products/enhanced-search?keyword=face%20mask&ratingMin=3&limit=15&offset=0

GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products/enhanced-search?category=Shampoo&priceMax=800&limit=10&offset=0
